---
---
<section id="who-its-for" class="px-6 py-20 md:py-28 border-t border-border">
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-5xl">
		<p class="eyebrow text-center">Who it's for</p>
		<h2 class="heading-lg text-center mt-3">Built for how you work</h2>
		<p class="body-lg text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mt-4">Whether you ship code, manage clients, or run a company — AEOrank fits your workflow.</p>

		<div class="space-y-6 mt-14">

			<!-- Developer Panel -->
			<div class="audience-card animate-on-scroll" style="--panel-color: #E8590C; --panel-glow: rgba(232,89,12,0.08); --panel-border: rgba(232,89,12,0.35);">
				<div class="audience-card__gradient-border"></div>
				<div class="audience-card__inner grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-10">
					<div>
						<p class="audience-eyebrow" style="color: #E8590C;">For Developers</p>
						<h3 class="heading-md mt-2">AEO in your pipeline. Not your browser.</h3>
						<p class="text-text-muted mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">The only AEO tool that lives in your terminal, your CI, and your framework — not a SaaS dashboard you forget to check.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-5">
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(232,89,12,0.12); color: #E8590C; border-color: rgba(232,89,12,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M4 17l6-5-6-5"/><path d="M12 19h8"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">CLI-first, zero magic</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1"><code class="!text-[10px]">npx aeorank-cli scan &lt;url&gt;</code> — runs anywhere, no account, no API key. Colored output with per-criterion scores.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(232,89,12,0.12); color: #E8590C; border-color: rgba(232,89,12,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M9 19c-5 1.5-5-2.5-7-3m14 6v-3.87a3.37 3.37 0 0 0-.94-2.61c3.14-.35 6.44-1.54 6.44-7A5.44 5.44 0 0 0 20 4.77 5.07 5.07 0 0 0 19.91 1S18.73.65 16 2.48a13.38 13.38 0 0 0-7 0C6.27.65 5.09 1 5.09 1A5.07 5.07 0 0 0 5 4.77a5.44 5.44 0 0 0-1.5 3.78c0 5.42 3.3 6.61 6.44 7A3.37 3.37 0 0 0 9 18.13V22"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Block AEO regressions in CI</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">GitHub App: one-click, zero YAML. GitHub Action: <code class="!text-[10px]">fail-below</code> thresholds. Both post Check Runs with full breakdowns.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(232,89,12,0.12); color: #E8590C; border-color: rgba(232,89,12,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="3" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="14" y="14" width="7" height="7"/><rect x="3" y="14" width="7" height="7"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">13 framework plugins, 3 lines of config</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Next.js, Astro, Nuxt, and 10 more. Serves all 9 generated files at your site root on build. MIT licensed, self-hostable.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-6">
						<div class="audience-quote-card" style="--quote-color: #E8590C;">
							<div class="audience-quote-mark" style="color: #E8590C;">"</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic leading-relaxed">"Dropped it in next.config.ts, ran the CI check, and caught a robots.txt regression before it shipped."</p>
							<footer class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-3">— Senior engineer, DevTools startup</footer>
							<div class="audience-metric" style="color: #E8590C;">
								<span class="audience-metric__number">411</span>
								<span class="audience-metric__label">tests. Same score every run.</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
							<a href="https://github.com/apps/aeorank" class="btn-primary justify-center text-sm">Install GitHub App</a>
							<a href="https://docs.aeorank.dev/getting-started" class="btn-secondary justify-center text-sm">Read the Docs</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Agency Panel -->
			<div class="audience-card animate-on-scroll" style="--panel-color: #6366F1; --panel-glow: rgba(99,102,241,0.08); --panel-border: rgba(99,102,241,0.35);">
				<div class="audience-card__gradient-border"></div>
				<div class="audience-card__inner grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-10">
					<div>
						<p class="audience-eyebrow" style="color: #818CF8;">For Agencies</p>
						<h3 class="heading-md mt-2">Client AI visibility reports. In 30 seconds per site.</h3>
						<p class="text-text-muted mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">Scan any client URL, get a scored report across 36 criteria, and deliver AI optimization as a service — using a free tool you can self-host.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-5">
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(99,102,241,0.12); color: #818CF8; border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Benchmark clients against competitors</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Our Scoreboard shows 100 funded startups averaging 42/100. Your clients are probably invisible to AI. Now you have the data to prove it.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(99,102,241,0.12); color: #818CF8; border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8z"/><polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Deliverable files, not dashboard links</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Every scan generates 9 production files — llms.txt, schema.json, ai.txt, robots patch. Hand them to the client. They deploy. You look like a wizard.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(99,102,241,0.12); color: #818CF8; border-color: rgba(99,102,241,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M18 20V10M12 20V4M6 20v-6"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Unlimited scans. $0 tool cost.</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">No per-seat pricing. No API credits. The CLI is MIT licensed. Scan 500 clients per month for free. Keep the margin.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-6">
						<div class="audience-quote-card" style="--quote-color: #818CF8;">
							<div class="audience-quote-mark" style="color: #818CF8;">"</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic leading-relaxed">"We added AEO audits to our SEO retainer. Clients love the score — they understand 67/100 immediately."</p>
							<footer class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-3">— Founder, boutique digital agency</footer>
							<div class="audience-metric" style="color: #818CF8;">
								<span class="audience-metric__number">42</span>
								<span class="audience-metric__label">/100 avg industry score</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
							<a href="https://docs.aeorank.dev/getting-started" class="btn-primary justify-center text-sm" style="background: #6366F1;">Scan a Client Site Free</a>
							<a href="/scoreboard" class="btn-secondary justify-center text-sm">See Industry Benchmarks</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

			<!-- Founder Panel -->
			<div class="audience-card animate-on-scroll" style="--panel-color: #EAB308; --panel-glow: rgba(234,179,8,0.08); --panel-border: rgba(234,179,8,0.35);">
				<div class="audience-card__gradient-border"></div>
				<div class="audience-card__inner grid md:grid-cols-[2fr_1fr] gap-10">
					<div>
						<p class="audience-eyebrow" style="color: #EAB308;">For Founders</p>
						<h3 class="heading-md mt-2">ChatGPT recommends your competitors. Not you.</h3>
						<p class="text-text-muted mt-3 text-sm leading-relaxed">AI search drives 40% of web discovery and converts at 15.9% — higher than Google. Your score tells you how visible you are. The generated files start fixing it immediately.</p>
						<ul class="mt-6 space-y-5">
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(234,179,8,0.12); color: #EAB308; border-color: rgba(234,179,8,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">A number you can actually act on</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">Your AEO score is 0–100, graded A+ through F. You see exactly which criteria you're failing and why. No vague advice — specific gaps, ranked by impact.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(234,179,8,0.12); color: #EAB308; border-color: rgba(234,179,8,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polyline points="22 7 13.5 15.5 8.5 10.5 2 17"/><polyline points="16 7 22 7 22 13"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">Your competitors are scoring 42/100 on average</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">We scanned 100 funded startups. Stripe scores 57. OpenAI scores 16. If billion-dollar companies are invisible to AI, your site probably is too — and it's fixable in an afternoon.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
							<li class="audience-list-item">
								<div class="audience-list-icon" style="background: rgba(234,179,8,0.12); color: #EAB308; border-color: rgba(234,179,8,0.2);">
									<svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><polygon points="13 2 3 14 12 14 11 22 21 10 12 10 13 2"/></svg>
								</div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-sm">30 seconds to your first score</p>
									<p class="text-text-muted text-xs mt-1">No account, no credit card, no sales call. Gartner predicts 50% decline in organic search traffic by 2028. This is the fix.</p>
								</div>
							</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col justify-between gap-6">
						<div class="audience-quote-card" style="--quote-color: #EAB308;">
							<div class="audience-quote-mark" style="color: #EAB308;">"</div>
							<p class="text-sm text-text-secondary italic leading-relaxed">"Had no idea AI couldn't see my site. Scored 31/100, fixed the llms.txt and schema, rescanned at 68 in one afternoon. Now we show up in Perplexity answers."</p>
							<footer class="text-xs text-text-muted mt-3">— Founder, B2B SaaS (pre-Series A)</footer>
							<div class="audience-metric" style="color: #EAB308;">
								<span class="audience-metric__number">31→68</span>
								<span class="audience-metric__label">in one afternoon</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
							<a href="https://github.com/apps/aeorank" class="btn-primary justify-center text-sm" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #CA8A04, #EAB308);">Check My Score — Free</a>
							<a href="/scoreboard" class="btn-secondary justify-center text-sm">See How Others Score</a>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>

		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	/* Card shell with gradient left border */
	.audience-card {
		position: relative;
		border-radius: 16px;
		overflow: hidden;
		transition: box-shadow 0.25s ease, transform 0.25s ease;
	}
	.audience-card:hover {
		transform: translateY(-2px);
		box-shadow: 0 20px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.4), 0 0 0 1px var(--panel-border);
	}

	/* Gradient left border using background-clip */
	.audience-card__gradient-border {
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		border-radius: 16px;
		background:
			linear-gradient(var(--color-bg-card), var(--color-bg-card)) padding-box,
			linear-gradient(180deg, var(--panel-border) 0%, transparent 100%) border-box;
		border: 1px solid transparent;
		border-left-width: 3px;
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 0;
	}

	/* Ambient glow from left border */
	.audience-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		top: 0;
		left: 0;
		width: 300px;
		height: 100%;
		background: radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 50%, var(--panel-glow) 0%, transparent 70%);
		pointer-events: none;
		z-index: 0;
	}

	.audience-card__inner {
		position: relative;
		z-index: 1;
		padding: 2rem 2.5rem;
	}

	.audience-eyebrow {
		font-size: 0.6875rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.1em;
	}

	/* List items */
	.audience-list-item {
		display: flex;
		gap: 1rem;
		align-items: flex-start;
	}
	.audience-list-icon {
		width: 30px;
		height: 30px;
		border-radius: 7px;
		border: 1px solid;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		flex-shrink: 0;
		margin-top: 1px;
	}

	/* Quote card */
	.audience-quote-card {
		position: relative;
		background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
		border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
		border-radius: 12px;
		padding: 1.25rem;
		overflow: hidden;
	}
	.audience-quote-card::before {
		content: '';
		position: absolute;
		inset: 0;
		background: linear-gradient(135deg, color-mix(in srgb, var(--quote-color) 5%, transparent) 0%, transparent 60%);
		pointer-events: none;
	}

	/* Big decorative quotation mark */
	.audience-quote-mark {
		font-size: 4rem;
		line-height: 0.6;
		font-family: Georgia, serif;
		opacity: 0.25;
		display: block;
		margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
	}

	/* Metric number with glow */
	.audience-metric {
		display: flex;
		align-items: baseline;
		gap: 0.375rem;
		margin-top: 1rem;
		padding-top: 0.75rem;
		border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
	}
	.audience-metric__number {
		font-size: 1.5rem;
		font-weight: 800;
		letter-spacing: -0.04em;
		line-height: 1;
		filter: drop-shadow(0 0 8px currentColor);
	}
	.audience-metric__label {
		font-size: 0.75rem;
		color: var(--color-text-muted);
		font-weight: 500;
	}
</style>
